      <title>“脆弱”的新西兰促使总理呼吁预算正统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/-fragile-new-zealand-prompts-pm-to-call-for-budget-orthodoxy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰总理克里斯托弗·卢克森在一次重要讲话中表示，新西兰处于“脆弱”状态，需要恢复公共财政秩序，这是建设更强大经济的先决条件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/-fragile-new-zealand-prompts-pm-to-call-for-budget-orthodoxy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 02:32:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
