      <title>经过近一周的抗议后，印度农民准备进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/indian-farmers-gear-up-for-talks-after-almost-week-of-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度北部数万名种植者抗议近一周后，印度农民将于周日与政府举行另一轮会谈，以帮助结束农作物价格争端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/indian-farmers-gear-up-for-talks-after-almost-week-of-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 02:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>降息预期推动买家购房，悉尼房屋拍卖激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/sydney-home-auctions-surge-as-rate-cut-expectations-drive-buyers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CoreLogic Inc.的数据显示，随着澳大利亚人越来越多地预计利率将会下降以及房价上涨加快，悉尼在拍卖中成功售出的房屋比例创下了两年多以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/sydney-home-auctions-surge-as-rate-cut-expectations-drive-buyers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 01:56:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于人民币回旋空间有限，中国保持关键利率稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/china-leaves-key-rate-steady-as-yuan-limits-maneuvering-room</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于央行试图保护人民币免受波动影响，中国没有下调关键政策利率，这突显了政策制定者在试图管理经济风险和通货紧缩压力时面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/china-leaves-key-rate-steady-as-yuan-limits-maneuvering-room</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 01:28:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数据乐观后，中国股市有望重新开盘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/china-stocks-primed-for-bullish-open-after-upbeat-holiday-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当境内交易者从农历​​新年假期回来时，中国股市似乎准备强劲开盘，强劲的旅行和旅游数据为全球表现最差的主要市场之一带来了急需的缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/china-stocks-primed-for-bullish-open-after-upbeat-holiday-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
