      <title>FTX 投资者起诉沙利文和克伦威尔，声称公司协助欺诈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-17/ftx-investors-sue-sullivan-cromwell-claiming-firm-aided-fraud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[FTX 投资者起诉沙利文咨询公司克伦威尔指责该律师事务所协助非法计划，这些计划在加密货币交易所崩溃之前帮助推进了数十亿美元的欺诈行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-17/ftx-investors-sue-sullivan-cromwell-claiming-firm-aided-fraud</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 19:25:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
